---
layout: base.njk
title: Services — Shot Okay Films
permalink: /services/
---
{% from "icons.njk" import serviceIcon %}

<div class="page-header wrap">
  <span class="eyebrow mono">WHAT WE SHOOT</span>
  <h1>Every story needs the right shot</h1>
  <p>Six kinds of visual stories, one studio. Pick a vertical below for the full breakdown, or just tell us what you need.</p>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  {% for s in services.services %}
  <div class="service-detail" id="{{ s.id }}">
    <div class="sd-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="sd-icon">{{ serviceIcon(s.icon) }}</div>
        <span class="sd-num mono">{{ s.cam }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sd-content">
        <h2>{{ s.name }}</h2>
        <p class="sd-headline">{{ s.headline }}</p>
        <p class="sd-desc">{{ s.longDescription }}</p>
        <a href="/contact/?service={{ s.name | urlencode }}" class="btn-outline">Get a quote for this</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Not sure which fits?</h2>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-rec">Tell us what you need</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
